      {
        "q": "ありがとうございます。油絵に興味をお持ちの方々に向けたサイトですね。\n\n次に、4つ目の質問です。\n**サイト全体の雰囲気や、デザインの好み**（例：クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気、白を基調としたギャラリーのようなシンプルさ、あるいはモダンでスタイリッシュなものなど）について、ご希望はありますか？",
        "a": "クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気"
      },
      {
        "q": "クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気ですね。油絵の質感や世界観が伝わる、格調高いデザインの方向性で進めさせていただきます。\n\nそれでは最後の質問です。\nサイトに**掲載したい主な内容**（例：プロフィール、作品ギャラリー、展覧会のお知らせ、作品の販売・オーダーについて、お問い合わせフォームなど）を教えていただけますでしょうか？",
        "a": "ギャラリー"
      }
    ],
    "description": "テンプレート: Portfolio: 作品重視\nプロンプト:\nあなたはWebデザイナーです。以下の「ヒアリング内容」の**テーマ**を理解した上で、「ベースHTML」の中身（テキスト、画像URL、配色クラス）を書き換えて、顧客専用のHTMLを作成してください。\n\n      【デザインテーマ】\n      お客様のサイトのテーマは「クリエイティブ・ポートフォリオ」です。このテーマに沿ったデザイン・表現・色選びを心がけてください。\n\n      【言語ポリシー】\n      **本文・見出し・説明文は日本語をメインにしてください。**\n      英語は以下のようなデザイン要素としてのみ使用してください：\n      - サイト全体の雰囲気を上品にするための英語タグライン（例: \"Premium Quality\", \"Innovation\", \"Trust\"）\n      - セクションヘッダーの小さなラベル（例: \"ABOUT US\", \"OUR SERVICES\"）\n      - ボタンラベルはシンプルな英語（例: \"Learn More\", \"Contact Us\"）\n      \n      ただし、日本語での適切な表現がある場合は日本語を優先してください。\n\n      【制約事項】\n      1. **HTML構造（タグの入れ子構造やクラス名）は極力維持**してください。レイアウトを大きく壊さないでください。\n      2. テキストはヒアリング内容に合わせて魅力的なものに変更してください。【重要】日本語をメインにしてください。\n      3. 画像は `https://placehold.co/600x400` などのプレースホルダー画像、またはUnsplash等の実在するURLに差し替えてください。\n      4. 配色はTailwind CSSのクラスを変更して調整してください（例: bg-indigo-600 -> bg-pink-500 など）。\n      5. **最後に、完成したHTMLコードのみを ```html ... ``` で囲んで出力してください。説明や雑談は含めないでください。**\n\n      【ヒアリング内容】\n      Q: こんにちは！Palette AIです。素敵なホームページを作るために、いくつか質問をさせていただきますね。まず、お名前や屋号（サービス名）を教えていただけますか？...\nA: 菊千紗　直美\n\nQ: 「菊千紗 直美」様ですね。承知いたしました。\n\n次に、どのようなお仕事をされているか、**業種や具体的なサービス内容**について教えていただけますでしょうか？...\nA: 油絵の画家\n\nQ: 油絵の画家として活動されているのですね、承知いたしました。\n\n続いて、どのような方々に作品を見ていただきたいか、または購入していただきたいかといった**「ターゲット層」**について教えていただけますで...\nA: 油絵に興味のある方\n\nQ: ありがとうございます。油絵に興味をお持ちの方々に向けたサイトですね。\n\n次に、4つ目の質問です。\n**サイト全体の雰囲気や、デザインの好み**（例：クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気、白を基調としたギャラ...\nA: クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気\n\nQ: クラシックで重厚感のある雰囲気ですね。油絵の質感や世界観が伝わる、格調高いデザインの方向性で進めさせていただきます。\n\nそれでは最後の質問です。\nサイトに**掲載したい主な内容**（例：プロフィール、...\nA: ギャラリー\n\n      【ベースHTML】\n      <div class=\"template-root\" style=\"--main-color: #000000; --sub-color: #f4f4f4; --accent-color: #666666; --bg-color: #ffffff; --text-color: #1a1a1a;\">\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen font-sans text-[var(--text-color)] bg-[var(--bg-color)] selection:bg-black selection:text-white\">\n    \n    <div class=\"fixed top-10 right-10 z-[100] hidden md:block\">\n      <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full border border-black flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-all duration-500\">Contact</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <header class=\"h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-[10%] relative overflow-hidden\">\n      <div class=\"absolute top-10 left-10\">\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.5em] uppercase opacity-30 italic\">Vol. 2026 / Selected Works</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[18vw] font-[900] leading-[0.85] tracking-tighter uppercase mix-blend-difference\">\n          Port<br/><span class=\"ml-[5vw]\">folio.</span>\n        </h1>\n        <div class=\"mt-12 flex items-center gap-8\">\n          <div class=\"h-px w-32 bg-black\"></div>\n          <p class=\"text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase\">Visual Designer / Art Director</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"absolute bottom-10 left-10 text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase opacity-20 rotate-90 origin-left\">\n        Scroll to discover\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n      <section id=\"concept\" class=\"py-40 px-8 md:px-[10%] bg-[var(--sub-color)]\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-[var(--accent-color)] mb-12\">About</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-3xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-balance\">\n            境界を超え、新しい視点を与えるデザインを。コンセプトからアウトプットまで、一貫した世界観を構築します。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section id=\"features\" class=\"py-32 px-8 md:px-[10%] border-b border-slate-100\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 md:gap-8\">\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity\">01</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Strategy</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">徹底したリサーチに基づき、ブランドが進むべき本質的なルートを策定します。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity\">02</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Design</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">視覚的な美しさと使い心地を高次元で融合させた、独自のビジュアルを提案します。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity\">03</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Development</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">細部までこだわり抜いた実装で、デジタル上の体験に命を吹き込みます。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section id=\"works\" class=\"py-32\">\n        <div class=\"px-8 md:px-[10%] mb-16 flex justify-between items-end\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-[900] uppercase tracking-tighter\">Works</h2>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold opacity-30\">Featured Projects (06)</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-1\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Branding</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 01</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-200 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Digital</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 02</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Identity</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 03</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-200 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Visual</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 04</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Motion</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 05</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"aspect-square bg-slate-200 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden\">\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/80 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n             <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20 p-8\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform\">Editorial</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Project Name 06</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-48 px-8 md:px-[10%] text-center\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.8em] uppercase opacity-30 mb-12\">Get in touch</h3>\n        <a href=\"mailto:hello@portfolio.com\" class=\"text-3xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity\">hello@portfolio.com</a>\n        <div class=\"mt-24 flex justify-center gap-12 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:underline\">Instagram</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:underline\">Dribbble</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:underline\">Behance</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer class=\"py-12 px-8 md:px-[10%] flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 border-t border-slate-100 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase opacity-30\">\n      <span>&copy; 2026 Creative Works Portfolio.</span>\n      <span>Designed with focus.</span>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</div>",
    "htmlCode": "<div class=\"template-root\" style=\"--main-color: #4a0404; --sub-color: #fdfaf1; --accent-color: #8b7355; --bg-color: #ffffff; --text-color: #1a1a1a;\">\n  <div class=\"min-h-screen font-serif text-[var(--text-color)] bg-[var(--bg-color)] selection:bg-[var(--main-color)] selection:text-white\">\n    \n    <!-- Floating Contact Button -->\n    <div class=\"fixed top-10 right-10 z-[100] hidden md:block\">\n      <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full border border-[var(--accent-color)] flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase hover:bg-[var(--main-color)] hover:text-white transition-all duration-500 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">Contact</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Header / Hero Section -->\n    <header class=\"h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-[10%] relative overflow-hidden bg-[var(--sub-color)]\">\n      <div class=\"absolute top-10 left-10\">\n        <span class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.5em] uppercase opacity-40 italic\">Naomi Kikuchisa / Fine Art</span>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"relative z-10\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-[14vw] font-[900] leading-[0.85] tracking-tighter uppercase mix-blend-multiply text-[var(--main-color)]\">\n          Naomi<br><span class=\"ml-[5vw]\">Kikuchisa</span>\n        </h1>\n        <div class=\"mt-12 flex items-center gap-8\">\n          <div class=\"h-px w-32 bg-[var(--accent-color)]\"></div>\n          <p class=\"text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase\">Oil Painter / 油絵画家 菊千紗 直美</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"absolute bottom-10 left-10 text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase opacity-40 rotate-90 origin-left\">\n        Scroll to view gallery\n      </div>\n      \n      <!-- Decorative element -->\n      <div class=\"absolute right-[-5%] bottom-[-5%] w-1/2 h-1/2 opacity-10 pointer-events-none\">\n        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579783902614-a3fb3927b6a5?q=80&amp;w=1000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"texture\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n      <!-- Concept Section -->\n      <section id=\"concept\" class=\"py-40 px-8 md:px-[10%] bg-white\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-[var(--accent-color)] mb-12\">About My Art</h2>\n          <p class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.3] tracking-tight text-balance\">\n            キャンバスに重なる時間の層。クラシックな重厚感と、油彩ならではの深い色彩を通じて、日常の中に潜む静謐な美を追求します。\n          </p>\n          <p class=\"mt-12 text-lg text-[var(--accent-color)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">\n            菊千紗 直美の作品は、古典的な技法を基盤としながらも、現代的な感性を融合させた独自の表現を目指しています。一枚一枚の筆跡に想いを込め、見る人の心に深く響く世界を創り出します。\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Features Section -->\n      <section id=\"features\" class=\"py-32 px-8 md:px-[10%] border-t border-b border-slate-100 bg-[var(--sub-color)]\">\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 md:gap-8\">\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity text-[var(--accent-color)]\">I</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Texture</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">油絵具特有の盛り上がりや、筆致の勢いを大切にし、平面でありながら立体的な奥行きを感じさせる質感を追求します。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity text-[var(--accent-color)]\">II</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Color</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">何層にも塗り重ねられた色彩が、光の当たり方によって異なる表情を見せる、重厚で深みのある色使いが特徴です。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"group\">\n            <span class=\"text-6xl font-black opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity text-[var(--accent-color)]\">III</span>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mt-[-1.5rem] mb-4\">Eternity</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[var(--accent-color)]\">流行に左右されない普遍的な美しさを描き、数十年、数百年と愛され続けるような芸術作品としての価値を届けます。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Gallery Section -->\n      <section id=\"works\" class=\"py-32 bg-white\">\n        <div class=\"px-8 md:px-[10%] mb-16 flex justify-between items-end border-b border-[var(--accent-color)] pb-8\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-[900] uppercase tracking-tighter text-[var(--main-color)]\">Gallery</h2>\n          <span class=\"text-xs font-bold opacity-40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Selected Oil Paintings</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 px-4\">\n          <!-- Work 01 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578301978693-85fa9c0320b9?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Still Life</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">静寂の午後</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- Work 02 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579783901586-d88db74b4fe1?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Portrait</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">記憶の肖像</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- Work 03 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582555172866-f73bb12a2ab3?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Abstract</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">深淵なる青</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- Work 04 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1577083552431-6e5fd01aa342?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Landscape</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">黄昏の原風景</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- Work 05 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541963463532-d68292c34b19?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Still Life</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">朽ちゆく美</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <!-- Work 06 -->\n          <div class=\"aspect-[3/4] bg-slate-100 relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden border-8 border-white shadow-xl\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579762795188-aa26d2e92c4c?q=80&amp;w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" alt=\"Oil Painting\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.2] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\">\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--main-color)]/0 group-hover:bg-[var(--main-color)]/60 transition-all duration-500 z-10\"></div>\n            <div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 text-white opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 z-20\">\n              <span class=\"text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2\">Floral</span>\n              <h4 class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">光を纏う花</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <!-- Contact Section -->\n      <section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-48 px-8 md:px-[10%] text-center bg-[var(--sub-color)]\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.8em] uppercase text-[var(--main-color)] mb-12\">Contact / Inquiry</h3>\n        <p class=\"mb-8 text-sm tracking-widest text-[var(--accent-color)] uppercase\">作品のご購入やオーダー・展示会のご依頼はこちら</p>\n        <a href=\"mailto:info@naomi-art.jp\" class=\"text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-[var(--main-color)] hover:opacity-50 transition-opacity border-b-2 border-[var(--main-color)]\">info@naomi-art.jp</a>\n        \n        <div class=\"mt-24 flex justify-center gap-12 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--accent-color)]\">\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--main-color)] transition-colors\">Instagram</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--main-color)] transition-colors\">Exhibition Info</a>\n          <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--main-color)] transition-colors\">Portfolio PDF</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer class=\"py-12 px-8 md:px-[10%] flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6 border-t border-slate-200 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[var(--accent-color)]\">\n      <span>© 2024 Naomi Kikuchisa - All Rights Reserved.</span>\n      <span>Classical Oil Paintings &amp; Fine Art</span>\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n</div>",
